snippet.textDisplay: Does anybody else feel like these two are growing apart? Rhett seems like he wants to become his own person, and it feels like there’s a divide between them. (No judgement on Rhett of course, I’m sure it’s incredibly difficult being known as only half of an entity.) There’s more tension and backbiting in GMM, less playing off one another. They just don’t seem like they’ve been enjoying their time together, and it’s been getting worse. Maybe it’s just me, or maybe it’s just a temporary thing, but it’s beginning to feel like they’re more interested in themselves than each other.
